				<outline text="A small release (0.2.8) to fix several annoying bugs.
&lt;a href=&quot;https://logseq.github.io/#/page/48e76d46-3419-455c-84a0-349b80e369b8&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/4L5oCoTJa2" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:25:52 GMT" tweetId="1418608311306375176" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1418608311306375176" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
